  "title": "A Family Party and a New View",
  "article_text": "I consider my local party for families at a low price. My parents often speak with other people at the party. We learn together within a group of our age. The process is hard for a person at a low level. It is possible to train for a better public view. Actually, the least experienced person can learn a new skill. There is a train at the local station for a trip. We view the park from a hill, and it is rather beautiful. The price of a ticket is low for a family. At the party, we consider the experience a good one once a year.",
